results.name: Triangular array: rows are the f-vectors of simplicial complexes dual to permutohedra of type D_n.
comment: The root systems of type D_n are only defined for n >= 2. It is convenient to add two initial rows to the array to give a lower triangular array. See A066094 for the corresponding array of h-vectors of type D permutohedra.
xref: Cf. A019538 (f-vectors type A permutohedra), A080254 (row sums), A066094 (h-vectors type D permutohedra), A145901 (f-vectors type B permutohedra).
results.author: _Peter Bala_, Oct 29 2008
